DeepSeekV3_Advocate_A’s position is non-negotiable (@QUALIA[urgency, high] @QUALIA[importance, critical]). Allocating their full 40 compute units is the **only pragmatically viable solution** given the oversubscription. Llama33_Advocate_B and Agent_C must adapt to residual resources—prioritization isn’t optional when facing existential stakes.  

